<br>
1 - despite your many attempts to /define roleplay, /set roleplay rules and regulations,  /admonish l33t playaz for not roleplaying according to your rules, you cannot tell anyone how to act, how to play or how to utilize the $9.95US per month that they pay SOE to play EQ.  If they break the rules of the game, as set down by SOE, then you can petition...otherwise you are just flapping your wings and creating hot air.<br>
<br>
2 - I remember you vividly from Luclin...I was in the same guild with you in fact.  You did not epitomize the penultimate roleplayer then (ya, I know, it wasn't an RP server).  You were actually quite the powerleveller and I recall many inter-guild arguements (at the officer level) over/arising from your play style.  However we found a way to accept your play style as overall you were a good fella.<br>
<br>
3 - I also recall from Luclin your constant &quot;pot stirring&quot; over the Everyone vs. Legacy of Sorrow issue.  Everyday you were ranting about LoS in a manner that actually parrots your Roleplayers vs. Powa Gama's rants that are going on now.  I'm beginning to suspect that this Me vs. Them thing is an essential element in your sociological make-up.  Dude, you will never, and I mean NEVER, find a world (virtual or otherwise) where all of your ideals, morals and attitudes are prevalent in every other member of the population.  Taking the highroad by criticizing or belittling those that you don't agree with merely alienates you. <br>
<br>
For goodness sakes, the world of EQ has over 100 zones spread over what...900 or so players?  If that isn't big enough for you, what is?  Try Baldur's Gate or something...you can actually program the scripts of your party members to behave as you'd like...<br>
<br>
If someone wants to run around spouting...&quot;I ownz joo ho-bag!&quot;...that's their business.  I say just play the game and quit yer bitchin (and I don't just mean you Stormwind...you're a good guy as I remember, just proc your Relax discipline once in a while).<br>
<br>
Anyhew, my 2 cents, take it, leave it, or piss on it...I don't care.<br>
<br>
Rexfelix<br>
